00:11:45.270 --> 00:11:46.980
Siguradong mabilis akong gagaling.

00:11:47.000 --> 00:11:47.860
♪Crush mo ♪

00:11:47.960 --> 00:11:48.750
Mula ngayon,

00:11:49.440 --> 00:11:51.000
alagaan mong mabuti ang iyong sarili.

00:11:51.100 --> 00:11:51.940
♪Itago mo sa sarili mo♪

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:53.600
Huwag na huwag mong hayaang madaling masaktan muli.

