00:14:27.680 --> 00:14:28.420
Ang.

00:14:29.460 --> 00:14:30.420
Sir.

00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:33.940
Panatilihing tuyo ang kanyang mga sugat

00:14:34.520 --> 00:14:35.660
